Look at me, boy.

02:30.976 --> 02:34.110
Cryin' ain't buyin'
in this world.

02:34.154 --> 02:37.809
All them cowboy books...

02:37.853 --> 02:41.291
none of 'em ever cries,
does they?

02:43.685 --> 02:47.906
Them boys that took your money,
they was older than you?

