23:17.439 --> 23:20.050
What do you think all them
switches are for?

23:20.094 --> 23:21.661
I don't know.

23:21.704 --> 23:23.271
Must be the bass or something.

23:23.314 --> 23:24.664
Whoa!

23:24.707 --> 23:26.579
- What the...
- Hey! Hold it!

23:26.622 --> 23:28.624
Hap! Hold the...

23:28.668 --> 23:30.626
Whoa!

23:30.670 --> 23:32.106
I am! I... Whoa! Aah!

23:32.149 --> 23:33.934
