24:00.439 --> 24:03.659
Flash flood warnings are
in effect for the entire region,

24:03.703 --> 24:05.792
and we just got word that
they're pumping out

24:05.835 --> 24:07.228
the Old Mill Dam

24:07.271 --> 24:09.143
to keep it from overflowing...

24:09.186 --> 24:12.799
unlike my radio station,
which seems like a wading pool.

24:12.842 --> 24:16.455
Yeah, kids,
stay home, no school,

24:16.498 --> 24:18.892
no buses, make some
hot chocolate,

24:18.935 --> 24:21.503
and drive your parents crazy.

24:21.547 --> 24:24.898
The Governor has declared
a state of emergency...

24:24.941 --> 24:27.466
and issued
a voluntary evacuation

24:27.509 --> 24:29.511
for all low-lying areas.

24:29.555 --> 24:32.383
I, Sonny Knox,
will keep you informed

24:32.427 --> 24:34.516
as the storm progresses.

24:34.560 --> 24:38.085
In the meantime, break out
the rowboats, life jackets,

24:38.128 --> 24:40.740
and settle down
for this classic riff.

24:40.783 --> 24:44.004
This one's coming to ya from.

24:44.047 --> 24:47.442
Brown's Christmas tree farm,
