Wow.

25:10.987 --> 25:14.208
I thought you guys got away,
you stay away.

25:14.251 --> 25:16.776
Hey, Maude. Man.

25:16.819 --> 25:19.343
I'm sorry about all the mess.

25:19.387 --> 25:22.172
Well, things get be fixed.

25:22.216 --> 25:23.652
People can't.

25:23.696 --> 25:26.307
We lookin' for Truman Brown.

25:26.350 --> 25:28.265
What for?

25:28.309 --> 25:31.791
Son of a bitch Brown
runs this town now.

25:31.834 --> 25:33.662
Got that ice queen Reynolds
in his pocket.

25:33.706 --> 25:35.925
This what America's
supposed to be?

25:35.969 --> 25:38.145
I don't wanna live here no more.

25:38.188 --> 25:40.626
You know where he is?

25:40.669 --> 25:42.584
He's still in town.

25:42.628 --> 25:44.238
Anybody with half a brain
be gone by now,

25:44.281 --> 25:47.241
but he was by here with
his boys this morning.

25:47.284 --> 25:50.592
Why.

25:50.636 --> 25:52.246
Finish what we started.

25:52.289 --> 25:54.074
You're gonna be outgunned.

25:54.117 --> 25:55.554
Cut a snake off by the head,

25:55.597 --> 25:57.294
the body ain't worth shit
no more, right?

25:57.338 --> 25:59.732
Well, I guess you boys
owe him some.

25:59.775 --> 26:01.429
'Bout time somebody
had the balls

26:01.472 --> 26:04.214
to stand up to that
son of a bitch.

26:04.258 --> 26:06.129
You heard from Bacon?

26:06.173 --> 26:08.131
No.

26:08.175 --> 26:09.872
But I heard that
Brown and Reynolds

26:09.916 --> 26:12.483
are lookin' for him.

26:12.527 --> 26:16.575
They look hard enough,
they gon' find him.

26:16.618 --> 26:18.315
That was Slim Harpo... Right.

26:18.359 --> 26:22.406
With "Raining in My Heart,"
coming at you from 96.6.

26:22.450 --> 26:24.844
I'll be holding the water
back with a barrel of blues

26:24.887 --> 26:28.195
and keeping y'all up to date on
the latest storm development.

26:28.238 --> 26:31.198
Come on. Bye, Maude.

26:45.299 --> 26:47.170
Just got a special request

26:47.214 --> 26:49.608
from Hap Collins
and Leonard Pine.

26:49.651 --> 26:53.220
The boys are back in town
and would like Mr. Truman Brown

26:53.263 --> 26:55.396
to know they will be
waiting for him

26:55.439 --> 26:57.746
at Tim's Rocket Garage.

26:57.790 --> 26:59.618
So bring your noisemakers

26:59.661 --> 27:01.750
and join the boys
from Laborde...

27:01.794 --> 27:04.927
for a bang bang
New Tear celebration.

27:06.537 --> 27:08.888
Go get 'em, boys.

27:08.931 --> 27:10.803
Nice knowing you.

27:30.779 --> 27:34.000
Somebody, I'm in here!

27:34.043 --> 27:35.871
Can anybody...

27:56.805 --> 27:59.547
Damn!

27:59.590 --> 28:01.941
Damn it!

28:06.902 --> 28:10.732
Please, somebody help me!

28:13.126 --> 28:17.565
Help me!

28:17.608 --> 28:20.089
Somebody help me!

29:59.319 --> 30:01.016
Say, Hap.

30:02.844 --> 30:05.368
Maybe we shouldn't stand
in front of the gas pump.

30:07.936 --> 30:09.459
Yeah.

30:09.503 --> 30:10.896
Good thinking, Leonard.

30:39.663 --> 30:43.319
Maybe Truman Brown don't
listen to the blues.

30:43.363 --> 30:45.713
Maybe he like to listen
to that old gospel music.

30:48.020 --> 30:51.284
Then again, maybe not?

30:59.727 --> 31:02.643
Maybe this wasn't such
a good idea.

31:04.819 --> 31:07.430
We can always go home
and roast some marshmallows.

31:07.474 --> 31:09.998
Watch some TV.

31:10.042 --> 31:12.348
We can call Charlie over
to give us a puppet show.

31:12.392 --> 31:15.656
Yeah. That's starting
to sound like a good idea.

31:15.699 --> 31:17.310
Hello.

31:48.950 --> 31:50.821
This ain't a hold up, is it?

31:50.865 --> 31:52.432
No.

31:52.475 --> 31:54.216
But if you know
what's good for ya,

31:54.260 --> 31:56.697
you'll clear out before
the shootin' starts.

31:56.740 --> 31:58.394
Shootin'?

31:58.438 --> 32:00.005
You seen Truman Brown
and his boys?

32:00.048 --> 32:03.225
No. But I heard about that
run-in you had with him.

32:03.269 --> 32:04.879
Let me just, drop this car,

32:04.923 --> 32:07.229
and I'll clear out faster
than a scalded cat.

32:07.273 --> 32:08.990
I don't wanna be here
if y'all are gonna tango

32:09.014 --> 32:10.972
with Brown and his boys.

32:11.016 --> 32:12.931
I'll be out of your hair
in a jiff.

32:22.941 --> 32:24.681
Get up. Get up!

32:24.725 --> 32:26.814
Aah! Please don't
hit me no more!

32:26.857 --> 32:28.685
Just tell me the truth. Tell me!

32:28.729 --> 32:31.862
What happened to Florida?!
Where is she?!

32:31.906 --> 32:33.516
Okay, I'll tell you.

32:33.560 --> 32:35.083
I'll tell you!

32:40.088 --> 32:42.308
Tim, I'm gonna need
another night.

32:48.401 --> 32:49.837
I found it.

32:49.880 --> 32:51.665
Bobby Joe's granddaddy's
lost song.

32:51.708 --> 32:54.146
Get an earful. Come on.

32:54.189 --> 32:56.017
Ooh!

32:56.061 --> 32:58.150
This is worth a whole lot
of money, isn't it?

32:58.193 --> 32:59.978
Yeah, Bobby Joe said so.

33:00.021 --> 33:02.284
This belongs
to Bobby Joe's family.

33:02.328 --> 33:04.852
Let me introduce into evidence
a different point of view...

33:04.895 --> 33:06.854
It belongs to whoever finds it.

33:06.897 --> 33:08.987
That's not how this works.

33:10.292 --> 33:11.946
Hold on. Just a second.

33:11.990 --> 33:13.774
Look, I'm willing to split
with you, 50/50.

33:13.817 --> 33:15.471
What do you say?
We'll be partners.

33:15.515 --> 33:18.518
It's not ours to sell.

33:18.561 --> 33:20.737
Okay, 40/60.

33:23.305 --> 33:24.872
Wait a minute.
Just wait a minute.

33:24.915 --> 33:27.527
You ain't thinkin'
this through, sweetie.

33:30.095 --> 33:32.445
Don't ever call me sweetie.

33:35.883 --> 33:37.972
Stop it!

33:46.285 --> 33:48.069
No! Aah!

33:52.378 --> 33:53.944
Why did you do it?

33:53.988 --> 33:55.207
It wasn't me. I swear to you.

34:01.865 --> 34:05.130
What the hell?

34:15.183 --> 34:17.664
You killed her,
you son of a bitch!

34:17.706 --> 34:19.708
Hey, we got to find her!

34:22.147 --> 34:25.367
I didn't kill her.
I-I didn't do it.

34:25.411 --> 34:29.241
It was an accident.
I swear, an accident.

34:45.605 --> 34:47.041
Jeez.

35:33.218 --> 35:35.283
Look, please don't hurt me
again! Please don't hurt me! Get up!

35:35.307 --> 35:36.743
I'm just.

35:36.786 --> 35:38.484
Come on. Take us to her.

35:38.527 --> 35:39.876
Yeah, okay. Okay. Take us to her.

35:47.754 --> 35:49.930
Which one?

35:49.973 --> 35:51.540
! Come on!
- I don't remember!

35:51.584 --> 35:54.282
It was dark. It was a mistake.
You better remember!

35:54.326 --> 35:56.676
It's one of these!
I think it was one of these!

35:56.719 --> 35:58.721
Shit!

35:58.765 --> 36:00.201
Aah! Come here!

36:00.245 --> 36:03.204
Which... goddamn... car?

36:03.248 --> 36:04.814
I don't know.

36:08.340 --> 36:09.602
Which one?!

36:09.645 --> 36:12.518
Hello!

36:12.561 --> 36:14.128
I don't know!

36:14.172 --> 36:16.348
He don't know, Hap.

36:16.391 --> 36:20.178
We gotta search each one.
Every single one!

36:22.310 --> 36:24.138
Goddamn it.

36:24.182 --> 36:27.185
Help!

36:28.621 --> 36:30.797
Florida?

36:30.840 --> 36:32.364
Florida!

36:32.407 --> 36:34.104
Hap!

36:34.148 --> 36:35.715
Hap, is that you?

36:35.758 --> 36:37.195
Florida

36:37.238 --> 36:39.240
Florida, where are ya?!

36:39.284 --> 36:41.677
Hang on there, baby!
You in here?

36:41.721 --> 36:43.201
Hap!

36:43.244 --> 36:44.637
- Hey, over here, Hap!
- Florida!

36:44.680 --> 36:46.247
Hap, she's in here! Hey!!

36:46.291 --> 36:48.031
Florida! Yeah!

36:48.075 --> 36:51.470
- Florida!
- Hold on now! Hold on!

36:51.513 --> 36:54.037
Come on.
Florida, baby, we're comin'.

36:54.081 --> 36:55.735
One, two, three!

36:55.778 --> 36:58.825
Aah! Hap! Hap!

36:58.868 --> 37:02.611
Baby. Come on.

37:05.571 --> 37:08.661
Baby, Baby. Florida, you...
You all right?

37:08.704 --> 37:11.272
My god. My god.

37:13.883 --> 37:15.711
You okay? God. Thank god.

37:15.755 --> 37:18.453
Hap.

37:20.760 --> 37:22.718
Get down. Get down over there!

37:34.077 --> 37:37.080
You just couldn't
let it be, could ya?

37:38.691 --> 37:40.910
You wanted to see me?

37:40.954 --> 37:43.261
Here I am!

38:05.587 --> 38:07.981
You boys are
a couple of bad pennies.

38:10.418 --> 38:12.420
And I hate pennies.

38:12.464 --> 38:14.074
Hold it right there, Reynolds!

38:21.690 --> 38:23.431
Drop your guns!

38:59.424 --> 39:03.079
Aah!

39:03.123 --> 39:05.821
Brown!

39:05.865 --> 39:09.390
You ain't gonna shoot me,
you son of a bitch!

39:13.481 --> 39:15.831
You a peace lover, boy!

39:24.274 --> 39:26.320
I ain't your boy.

39:35.982 --> 39:37.897
Please, don't!

39:39.420 --> 39:40.813
It was Brown!

39:40.856 --> 39:42.771
He hung Bobby Joe,
him and Reynolds!

39:42.815 --> 39:46.819
Please, don't kill us!

39:46.862 --> 39:48.821
You scum ain't worth killin'.

39:54.914 --> 39:57.830
Run! Run!

39:57.873 --> 39:59.309
My god.

40:00.876 --> 40:03.444
Florida! Run! Run!

40:03.488 --> 40:05.794
Come on, get in the car!
Come on.

40:05.838 --> 40:07.883
- Bacon, get in the car, quick!
- Run! Come on!

40:07.927 --> 40:11.713
Get in there! Get in the car.

40:11.757 --> 40:14.934
Get in.

41:38.670 --> 41:40.933
I'm all right. I'm all right.

41:43.588 --> 41:45.024
Hap!

41:45.067 --> 41:46.416
Hap!

41:46.460 --> 41:48.331
Come on! Come on.

41:51.683 --> 41:54.642
God! God!

41:54.686 --> 41:56.644
God. God.

41:56.688 --> 41:58.167
Damn.

42:07.481 --> 42:11.267
Hey. Hey.

42:11.311 --> 42:12.747
Come here.

43:27.256 --> 43:29.258
They say three things
can't be hidden...

43:32.174 --> 43:34.133
the sun,

43:34.176 --> 43:36.918
the moon,

43:36.962 --> 43:38.572
and the truth.

43:40.966 --> 43:43.664
Hate makes ya blind...

43:48.147 --> 43:49.583
and hope breaks your heart.

43:52.630 --> 43:54.632
Hap Collins found out
the hard way.

44:01.421 --> 44:03.553
Only people do.

